   _[28]'White Russian Beauty'_
   [29]Yandy.com appears to have changed the name of the "White Russian Beauty"
   costume to "Russian Costume." (Is that better or worse? At least the
   original was an alcoholic beverage, and thus perhaps a pun costume.) More
   than anything, this costume is inaccurate: The sickle and hammer logo on the
   hat is out of date, and everyone knows "sexy Russians" have [30]red hair and
   do their seducing in lingerie, not figure skating costumes. If you already
   bought this costume, douse yourself in alcohol and go as the beverage
   instead. [Yandy]
