   _Nazis_
   Do not dress up like a Nazi. This costume is especially ill-advised if you
   are the prince of England, a [34]Republican nominee for Congress, or a
   [35]reality star who just broke the heart of America's sweetheart. If you
   already bought your Nazi costume, go to hell. OK, fine, you could also tell
   everyone you're not a Nazi, but Prince Harry dressed up as a Nazi. But if
   you run into anyone dressed up as the Bear Jew, look out.
     Links:
       34. http://gawker.us1.list-manage.com/track/click?u=251e609e1dba3888b86c21cc8&id=6ee4f93887&e=ec29360622
